  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "what_is_conditional",
      "title_en": "What Is Conditional Probability?",
      "title_he": "מה זה הסתברות מותנית?",
      "level_min": "3pt",
      "body_en_md": "New information changes the odds. **Conditional probability** asks: *given that A happened, how likely is B?*\n\nWe write $P(B \\mid A)$ — \"probability of $B$ **given** $A$.\"\n\n**Weather:** Overall rain might be 20%, but **given** cloudy skies it jumps to 60%.\n\n**Cards:** After a red card is drawn, the deck changed — that is conditional thinking.",
      "body_he_md": "מידע חדש משנה סיכויים. *בהינתן ש-A קרה, מה הסיכוי ל-B?*\n\n$P(B \\mid A)$.\n\n**מזג אוויר:** מעונן → סיכוי גשם עולה.\n\n**קלפים:** אחרי שליפה — החפיסה השתנתה."
    },
    {
      "id": "formula",
      "title_en": "The Formula",
      "title_he": "הנוסחה",
      "level_min": "3pt",
      "body_en_md": "$$P(B \\mid A) = \\frac{P(A \\cap B)}{P(A)}$$\n\n**Bag:** 5 red, 3 blue. Draw red **without replacement**. $P(\\text{2nd red} \\mid \\text{1st red}) = \\frac{4}{7}$.\n\nFormula check: $P(A)=\\frac58$, $P(A\\cap B)=\\frac58\\cdot\\frac47$ → $P(B\\mid A)=\\frac47$.",
      "body_he_md": "$$P(B \\mid A) = \\frac{P(A \\cap B)}{P(A)}$$\n\n5 אדומות, 3 כחולות, בלי החזרה: $\\frac47$."
    },
    {
      "id": "tree_diagrams",
      "title_en": "Tree Diagrams",
      "title_he": "עצי הסתברות",
      "level_min": "3pt",
      "body_en_md": "For multi-stage experiments, draw a **tree**:\n\n```\n        Start\n       /     \\\n   H(1/2)   T(1/2)\n  /\n roll die → 1..6 (each 1/6)\n```\n\n**Multiply** along a path (AND). **Add** separate paths (OR).\nExample: $P(H \\text{ then } 4) = \\frac12 \\cdot \\frac16 = \\frac{1}{12}$.",
      "body_he_md": "**עץ הסתברות** לניסוי בשלבים.\n\nכפל לאורך מסלול (וגם), חיבור מסלולים (או)."
    },
    {
      "id": "independence",
      "title_en": "Independence",
      "title_he": "אי-תלות",
      "level_min": "3pt",
      "body_en_md": "$A$ and $B$ are **independent** if $P(A \\cap B) = P(A) \\cdot P(B)$.\n\n**Independent:** two coin flips.\n**Not independent:** cards without replacement.\n\n**Test:** if independent, $P(A \\mid B) = P(A)$.",
      "body_he_md": "**עצמאיים** אם $P(A \\cap B) = P(A)P(B)$.\n\nמטבעות: כן. קלפים בלי החזרה: לא."
    },
    {
      "id": "worked_exam_problem",
      "title_en": "Total Probability",
      "title_he": "הסתברות מלאה",
      "level_min": "3pt",
      "body_en_md": "**Box 1:** 3 white, 2 black. **Box 2:** 1 white, 4 black. Pick a box ($P=0.5$ each), draw one ball.\n\n$P(\\text{white}) = 0.5 \\times \\frac{3}{5} + 0.5 \\times \\frac{1}{5} = 0.3 + 0.1 = 0.4$\n\n**Total probability** — add all paths to \"white.\" Show each multiplication on the exam!",
      "body_he_md": "**קופסה 1:** 3ל 2ש. **קופסה 2:** 1ל 4ש. $P=0.5$ לכל קופסה.\n\n$P(\\text{לבן}) = 0.5 \\times \\frac35 + 0.5 \\times \\frac15 = 0.4$"
    }
  ],
